comment_data.body:
This is a potential compromise:

```cpp
const char *stream_desc = NULL;

switch (chan->streamtype) {
case kChannelStreamStdio:
  stream_desc = "stdio";
  break;
case kChannelStreamSocket:
  stream_desc = "socket";
  break;
}

if (stream_desc == NULL) {
  abort();
}
```

